reviews.text: The food is good, only the remodel not too good.

This place has some history in sai kung, worth eating for it's price and they serve quite good local food, consider sai kung already has pretty bad food in general, according to my 8 yrs experience living in the area. However, the biggest turn off of this place is the elder lady who works here always take away you plate before you finish eating, 9 out of 10 times. -_-"
